{"tid":2004790,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城兩房則王1300萬沽　不足一周賣貴1球","createTime":"2020-05-06T16:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T05:47:14.000Z","uid":267488,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"05d14d718860dd6263b880beceac7d278cb7a1ce","tid":2004790,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"中原潘浩其表示，鰂魚涌太古城5月暫錄得9宗成交，其中天星閣高層A室，實用面積580方呎，兩房則王間隔，享全海景，附有裝修，以1,300萬港元交吉易手，呎價22,414元，再創今年同類型標準戶新高。<br />\n<br />\n潘指，新買家為用家，原業主於2002年6月以265萬元買入，持貨18年現帳面獲利1,035萬元，單位升值3.9倍。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，太古城兩房則王做價，月初售1,200萬元已創今年最高紀錄，其後再錄一宗1,220萬元的買賣，至今樓價不足一星期已躍升100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n不足一星期升100萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc4617fd2edf8c93322af18056cccdb728dd9f9","tid":2004790,"uid":96321,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPM3kgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPM3kgh.png&h=b997b862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同則2年前唔係賣到就2萬4咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf4e5740a61618ea8a8e5b88114129773af5dec","tid":2004790,"uid":88329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdc4617fd2edf8c93322af18056cccdb728dd9f9","tid":2004790,"uid":96321,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPM3kgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPM3kgh.png&h=b997b862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同則2年前唔係賣到就2萬4咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"再創今年同類型標準戶新高。"},{"pid":"c236c594bbe7708f7a1cbe6d22e9dffb8a143001","tid":2004790,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bdc4617fd2edf